  ('The key distinction between prokaryotic and eukaryotic cells is ___.',['size only','presence of a cell wall','absence vs. presence of a nucleus: prokaryotes (bacteria) have no membrane-bound nucleus; eukaryotes (animals, plants, fungi) have a defined nucleus enclosed by a membrane','number of chromosomes'],2),
